To develop/run inside IDEA use "Import Project", select this directory, then select
"Import Project From External Model" and finally "SBT". After that you can right-click
the "DayNN" or "DayNNTests" scala classes and select "Run".

To develop/run from command line, use:

    $ sbt run
    $ sbt test

    # run a specific program
    $ sbt 'runMain Problem001'

    # run a specific test case
    $ sbt 'test-only -- ProblemNNNTests.verifyEdgeCases'

    # run certain tests based on a wildcard
    $ sbt 'test-only -- *ProblemNNN*'

    # run tests without color output
    $ sbt 'test-only -- -n'
